rComments: I'm not a WGS major/minor but i needed a SSc credit. She reads off a paper the entire lecture, but tbh who cares lol? Shes a VERY EASY marker. I'm pretty sure everyone in my class got at least a B. No tests. & y'all are tripping..... the final exam was easy if you read her chapter notes that she provides or read the textbook as expected of you

Professor Abdulnour's lectures were amazing; I learned a lot! She genuinely cares about her students. Her exams are brutal, but you can get an A if you show up to her lectures and study the slides/notes well. All questions were covered in her lectures/notes. I have also taken Biometrics (BIO360) with her, so I highly recommend all her courses.

The entire course is very simple, easy to teach yourself if you don't understand. However, the final exam was next to impossible, and every student that took the final exam felt that they had guess their way through it!
